      <description>Preconditions Having sent a message to customer service from FO
using the order.
Steps For a customer thread :
mark as &amp;ldquo;handled&amp;rdquo;=&amp;gt; The status is &amp;ldquo;red&amp;rdquo;
mark as &amp;ldquo;pending 1&amp;rdquo;=&amp;gt; The status is &amp;ldquo;brown&amp;rdquo;
mark as &amp;ldquo;pending 2&amp;rdquo;=&amp;gt; The status is &amp;ldquo;brown&amp;rdquo;
mark as &amp;ldquo;re-opened&amp;rdquo;=&amp;gt; The status is &amp;ldquo;Green&amp;rdquo;
Check that status was indeed changed
forward this discussion, check mail if well sent</description>
